  "content": "<p data-pid=\"-Wt0FJNq\">自己做卡片当然还是选 Anki，甚至是 SuperMemo。</p><p data-pid=\"jYscrLP2\">毕竟离线编辑+学习，意味着完全不需要网络。我高三一年，就是拿着一部没有卡的手机背 Anki ，这么过来的：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/34881368\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-608c64b63b8de3f705632ab6c27834d8_120x160.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1440\" data-image-height=\"2560\" class=\"internal\">叶峻峣：某高三学生的「Anki」使用心得</a><p data-pid=\"Ql3a6gwo\">另外，Anki 的插件可以实现很多不错的功能。比如图片遮挡、文字转语音、学习数据分析等等。</p><p data-pid=\"mFzoNngQ\">还有可以提前复习、适合考前突击的筛选牌组：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/94067520\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d28d0ab92b4b5442f13e9f3393c0a19d_ipico.jpg\" data-image-width=\"667\" data-image-height=\"594\" class=\"internal\">弥乱：[实用]蓝色牌组:啊哈哈哈,高阶魔法</a><p data-pid=\"CV43LBhj\">当然，不喜欢折腾、想直接用别人的卡片直接背的话，选记乎也不错。不过类似的产品挺多的，比如记一、Quizlet、拾忆笔记等等。好像还有其它的软件，也有不少停止运营了。（Anki 倒是不用担心停止运营，毕竟是国际开源项目，顶多不能用同步服务）</p><p data-pid=\"KbritM5D\">记乎的算法，估计也是 sm2 那一套吧，模板则是 Anki 那一套？</p><p data-pid=\"dfypxmg2\">另外用别人做的卡片，最好先理解再记忆，Anki 的操作请看这篇：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/168386543\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-04d8d795b54c5ecd480bb315b867745f_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"3508\" data-image-height=\"2480\" class=\"internal\">叶峻峣：【经验】他人牌组食用指北|Anki</a><p data-pid=\"Gw00552g\">利益相关：</p><p data-pid=\"SzL6oJUB\">Anki 3 年用户</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-31af862daacf3657fc448141b55ddace_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1603\" data-rawheight=\"979\" data-original-token=\"v2-cc539580e704d1e04a7833bf06bc4775\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9035514f0ad8551e82b873a01a3c62fc_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1603\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-31af862daacf3657fc448141b55ddace_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1603&#39; height=&#39;979&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1603\" data-rawheight=\"979\" data-original-token=\"v2-cc539580e704d1e04a7833bf06bc4775\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9035514f0ad8551e82b873a01a3c62fc_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1603\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-31af862daacf3657fc448141b55ddace_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-31af862daacf3657fc448141b55ddace_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"xdcxSNFJ\">Anki 高考专栏主编兼作者：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b08f3f097722d981e0357ff305adbe8c_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1530\" data-rawheight=\"880\" data-original-token=\"v2-66df34c4f3755e91cc72c0d55e5169c3\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-606b0281fc2e231ce8155f176b1eb15a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1530\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b08f3f097722d981e0357ff305adbe8c_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1530&#39; height=&#39;880&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1530\" data-rawheight=\"880\" data-original-token=\"v2-66df34c4f3755e91cc72c0d55e5169c3\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-606b0281fc2e231ce8155f176b1eb15a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1530\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b08f3f097722d981e0357ff305adbe8c_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b08f3f097722d981e0357ff305adbe8c_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"-AiwSNT4\">顺便问一下记乎老板 <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/b6153b48bf14d94ebb7a7109855bb7e8\" data-hash=\"b6153b48bf14d94ebb7a7109855bb7e8\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$b6153b48bf14d94ebb7a7109855bb7e8\">@亮亮</a> ，记乎啥时支持公式啊。。。我的高考牌组和大学牌组还等着搬过去呢。。。</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-a13ee0a8373dde77ea418c0d3122fd42_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"926\" data-rawheight=\"452\" data-original-token=\"v2-43632f16a5758d8050d6369d477edb58\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-92755db3896be0ba2b6dd063257cd93f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"926\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-a13ee0a8373dde77ea418c0d3122fd42_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;926&#39; height=&#39;452&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"926\" data-rawheight=\"452\" data-original-token=\"v2-43632f16a5758d8050d6369d477edb58\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-92755db3896be0ba2b6dd063257cd93f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"926\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-a13ee0a8373dde77ea418c0d3122fd42_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-a13ee0a8373dde77ea418c0d3122fd42_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-4cd0674ea1928dcb084cb5a2f23abbd1_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1393\" data-rawheight=\"831\" data-original-token=\"v2-21f8c9b7968aaeabe2f9eb0bbb5a897a\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-24bc3bca627fb99477fe59577df8f87e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1393\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4cd0674ea1928dcb084cb5a2f23abbd1_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1393&#39; height=&#39;831&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1393\" data-rawheight=\"831\" data-original-token=\"v2-21f8c9b7968aaeabe2f9eb0bbb5a897a\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-24bc3bca627fb99477fe59577df8f87e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1393\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4cd0674ea1928dcb084cb5a2f23abbd1_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-4cd0674ea1928dcb084cb5a2f23abbd1_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p></p>",
